packages/docs/src/self-hosting/users-authentication-key-generator.md
    44→# User Authentication Key Generator
    46→This tool generates the value for the `AUTHENTICATION_USERS` environment variable. This variable is used to define the users that can authenticate to the application. The value should be a comma-separated list of email and password pairs, where the password is hashed using bcrypt.
    47→
    48→<CredentialInputs v-model="credentials" />
    49→
    50→```txt-vue
    51→AUTHENTICATION_USERS={{ envValue }}
    52→```
    53→
    54→<Toggle v-model="shouldEscapeWithDollar">
    55→    Escape for Docker Compose (use <code>$$</code> instead of <code>$</code>)
