packages/lib/README.md
     1→### Enclosed lib
     5→## Installation
     7→```bash
     8→# with npm
     9→npm install @enclosed/lib
    10→
    11→# with yarn
    12→yarn add @enclosed/lib
    13→
    14→# with pnpm
    15→pnpm add @enclosed/lib
    16→```
    17→
    18→## Usage
    20→```javascript
    21→import { createNote } from '@enclosed/lib';
    22→
    23→const { noteUrl } = await createNote({
    24→  content: 'Hello, World!',
    25→  password: 'password',
    26→  ttlInSeconds: 3600,
    27→  deleteAfterReading: true,
    28→});
    29→
    30→console.log(noteUrl);
    31→```
    32→
